headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 3X GTA$ and RP on Smuggler Sell Missions and More
content:
Sitting on a hoard of deadstock cargo in your Hangar? Don't let it sit there and gather dust. Offloading precious contraband in Smuggler Sell Missions between now and March 2 will net you a tripled payday.

Plus, Trap Door is claustrophobic blood-sport at its finest: armed teams compete for a spot on a rapidly-dwindling platform high above the waves of the Pacific. Whether you come out on top or tumble to your doom in the deep, all competitors walk away with 2X GTA$ and RP this week.
